# Example needles file for the pre-push private-content guard.
# Copy this to .preflight-needles (which is gitignored) and fill in your own
# markers. One extended-regex (grep -E) per line. Lines starting with # are comments.
#
# The guard (scripts/preflight.sh) scans outbox/ specs/ corpus/ EXAMPLE-*/ for
# these markers so your private content never leaks into the repo. The tracked
# script ships NO private literals - they all live in your local .preflight-needles.
#
# CRITICAL: never put a live secret in a tracked file. Keep tokens, internal
# domains, and private names in the gitignored .preflight-needles ONLY.
#
# Examples (edit for your own system):
# /Users/your-username
# \byour-internal-project\b
# your-internal-domain\.com
# <a-32-plus-char-api-token-value>
